{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act23side", "eventName": "登臨意", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "WB-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "風雨欲來", "storyInfo": "截雲在城中徘徊，等待出城的時機，也好奇地打量著這個陌生的移動城市。另一方面，這一切的幕後主使主動出現在林雨霞面前。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g1_yumenstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日漸西斜。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人和城牆的影子都被拉得很長。影子蓋過了路邊的鋪面，店家便收起陽傘，伸了一個漫長的懶腰。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後幾件，七折清倉，賣完回家吃飯嘍——", "name": "慵懶的攤販"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回去吧，還惦記著賣你那沒開刃的兵器模型啊，現在的遊客早就不吃那套了。", "name": "無聊的攤販"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要真會鑄劍的手藝，肯定也得去軍營裡做些大事。", "name": "慵懶的攤販"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，昨天我還真見到一個遊客佩著一把赤紅色的劍，看起來真不一般。也不知道是從哪搞來的......", "name": "無聊的攤販"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女茫然地看著四周。眼前盡是從未見過的景象。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腳下地面傳來隱隱的震動感，大概是移動城市減速的徵兆。但路上的行人卻似乎習以為常，有條不紊地做著平常的事。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚飯的香氣鑽入鼻腔。少女這才想起，自己已經整整兩天沒有吃過東西。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "渾身的酸痛隨著餓意一起襲來。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙腿也不聽自己使喚，跟著香味走向了一家飯館。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g04_yaninn", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客人要點什麼？", "name": "夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旁邊那桌人吃的......我也要一樣的。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，三號桌烤肉涼麵一份——", "name": "夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臨近晚飯的時間，店裡已經差不多坐滿。對於樸實的人們來說，忙碌了一天后，一頓踏實的晚飯，就是最好的慰藉。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牆上的電視機裡迴圈播放著刀光劍影的故事，偶有食客抬起頭，被熟悉的橋段吸引一陣注意力。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這個盒子裡的人，為什麼看起來和他一模一樣？）", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他旁邊的女俠，和師父有點像，又不太像......）", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（“故事由真實事件改編”又是什麼意思......）", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassclink"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客官您的麵來了，慢用。", "name": "夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝......謝謝。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就說應該送一幅百米長卷，讓城裡每個人都簽上名字，這樣的餞別禮物才有意義！", "name": "居民A"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不是傻，宗師是要走的，這麼大一件東西你讓他怎麼帶得走？", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正都是心意，不如多備點我們這裡的特色美食，還實在一點。", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說......那位宗師到底守了玉門多少年？", "name": "居民A"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體我也說不清楚，只知道我爹那一輩的人出生的時候，宗師就已經守在這了。", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他豈不是已經有一百多歲了？怪不得要離任，應該是身體吃不消了吧。", "name": "居民A"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我聽一些江湖人說，就在前陣子還有人見過他。看上去就是一副平常中年男人的樣貌。", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位宗師，不是正常人......？", "name": "居民A"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說這世上有些人，就是有用法術延年益壽的本事，宗師他大概也是吧。", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管他到底是什麼人，我們只要記得他是守護玉門城的大英雄，住在這的人，都應該記著他的好。", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只可惜，從來沒有聽說宗師他有過婚配，或是有一兒半女的。明明左將軍的公子都這麼大了，真是......", "name": "居民B"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他們說，那個人是......英雄？）", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#8$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姑娘，這飯也吃完了......還算合口味？", "name": "夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，很好吃。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這飯錢......", "name": "夥計"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_303_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來付吧。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝、謝謝你......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒沒什麼啦......真巧，又見面了。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是弄丟了錢包，還是忘了帶夠錢？", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......弄丟了......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？真倒楣。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來你也是剛來的樣子，應該對這裡也不熟悉。我和你一起去報官吧。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你的好意，還是不用了！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次的飯錢，我回頭會還給你的！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一等。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你帶著的這把劍......就是你之前說過，要找的那把？", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要搶嗎？！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼會平白無故搶別人的東西......", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我聽說，最近城中有一把很特殊的劍失竊，該不會就是......", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先告辭了。", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g13_yanlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人......？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出來！", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#7$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說不能和習武之人開這種玩笑。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況是世上所有習武之人裡練得最刻苦、最厲害的那個。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他要是一個條件反射，閉著眼對我一拳揮過來，我是不是就要交待在這了？", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我也只好把他抓起來，判一個過失殺人。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梁大人，怎麼說，剛才那個賭該算我贏了？", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......確實。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才和梁洵打賭，就賭你進門看見我倆是什麼反應。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他賭你會扭頭就走，我賭你會愣在原地一句話都講不出來。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "論看人的本事，我也從來沒見過有誰能勝過你。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況還不是別人，是我的結義兄弟。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，槐琥不知道你在這。", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是再不解風情，也知道該為父女重逢好好準備一個合適的場合。", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不像旁邊這位知府大人，有十幾年沒見面，找我的第一件事就把我捲進了一個天大的麻煩。", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那件事，的確是我虧欠你的......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再數落你，算不算指桑駡槐？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，這沒有別人，就我們三兄弟......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我準備了酒和菜，坐下來聊聊？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g10_yumenfair", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按小姐給的情報，所有可疑倉庫的地址都發到你們的終端上了。", "name": "龍門遊客？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從東到西，一個個去查。時間緊張，手腳快一點。", "name": "龍門遊客？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "查到情況不要輕舉妄動，先跟大夥聯絡，我們一起——", "name": "龍門遊客？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在找我？", "name": "孟鐵衣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！", "name": "龍門遊客？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那人反應很快，在道上摸爬滾打了許多年，他分得清什麼時候該打，什麼時候該逃。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 17.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是他剛轉過身去，就察覺到一隻手輕輕搭在他的肩頭，僅是這樣，他就再也動彈不得。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_033", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_789_1#10$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_789_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然要找我，為什麼又要逃？", "name": "孟鐵衣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_789_1#10$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......", "name": "龍門遊客？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_789_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小夥子辦事挺機靈，但少了點膽魄。改了這個毛病，將來或許能另有成就。", "name": "孟鐵衣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_789_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人緩緩收回了手。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_789_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去告訴你家林特使，今天申時正，城南五街七坊倉庫。我等她。", "name": "孟鐵衣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_789_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "250,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g13_yanlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不喝？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒到下班的時間。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不喝？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底對身體不好。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不喝酒，也不說話，這三雙眼睛乾瞪著算怎麼回事......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梁大人剛剛不還說有話要問他？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不也一樣。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#9$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之間不借酒，有些話也說不出口了嗎？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有話直說。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這些年......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊歷四方。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#3$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到一個地方就找能一戰的對手，直到找不到為止。然後就再換一個地方。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前見到梁大人，我還要細細揣摩一下這些年他的變化。槐武癡的變化，倒是直接寫在臉上了。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡變了？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#12$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老了。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是廢話。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也真的擔心過，要是哪天突然得知你死於和別人的交手。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有道是，人外有人......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你最終到了玉門......有多久了？", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三年。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡有人答應與我比武。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "短則三五年，長則十餘年。他是這麼說的。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當初說要爭一個天下聞名的槐天裴，居然也會這樣......耐得住寂寞。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正找不到別的對手，在這邊等幾年又何妨。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就在這家醫館當了三年夥計。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "酒倒入杯中，香氣卻被藥味蓋過。酒入愁腸，嘴裡只剩苦味。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“白頭翁”“刀傷木”“羽不泊”“千里及”......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在玉門武行打聽了大半月，卻怎麼也沒有想到，你就在客棧對面的這家醫館裡。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欠了債，總是要還的。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#8$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你也該清楚，在這世上你虧欠最多的人是誰。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#2$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得，我要說的話已經說完了，梁大人還有什麼話要問？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來探望老朋友，看看他過得怎麼樣，不該算“問話”。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "槐天裴在玉門待了三年，你來到玉門也有些時日，偏偏選這個時候來探望......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城中風波未定，不是顧及私情的時候。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梁大人一心為國，還不允許我們這些老百姓有些私情了？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎能......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#9$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們要是誠心想敘舊，我就再坐上一會。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說句話也不自在，我們怎麼變成了這副樣子？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "槐天裴端起了面前的酒，一飲而盡，轉身離開了房間。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梁大人，得到想要的答案了？", "name": "老鯉"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是作為槐天裴的義弟，還是作為玉門參知？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也該習慣了總是被你看透。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#8$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你該改改總是招攬麻煩事的習慣，至少別讓自己連個能說話的人都找不到。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一件事，他或許是恰當的人選......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像上次你挑我來送那個盞？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒那麼複雜......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還是那個槐天裴。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是最難變的。", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你我呢。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梁洵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_295_1#7$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欲買桂花同載酒，終不似，少年游。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還能坐在一張桌子上聊上幾句喝一杯酒，就已經是難能可貴的事。非要找回過去的那段日子，反倒像是刻舟求劍了。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g6_yumengate", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要攔我？", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩天發生了許多事，我也沒有搞太清楚。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你沒有惡意，最好能留下來，幫忙把事情說清楚。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有時間......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "交出手裡的東西。", "name": "山海眾成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休想！", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#5$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人是跟著你過來的？", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不認識他們......", "name": "截雲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4078_bdhkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天，在城裡到處作亂的人，就是你們？", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "av